property_value: IAO:0000600 "b is a site means: b is a three-dimensional immaterial entity that is (partially or wholly) bounded by a material entity or it is a three-dimensional immaterial part thereof. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [034-002])" xsd:string {IAO:0010000="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/034-002"}
