[Term]
id: OHD:0010288
name: constant unilateral facial pain with additional attacks (CUFPA)
def: "Constant (unremitting) dull unilateral facial pain of mild to moderate intensity, accompanied by distinct attacks of moderate to severe pain in the same location lasting 10--30 minutes. There are no typical autonomic and/or migrainoid features accompanying either the constant pain or the additional pain attacks." []
